<h1>Welcome to the Trans History Archive</h1>

<p>This archive documents significant events, people, and milestones in the history of trans identities. Our goal is to preserve and share this important history for education and awareness.</p>

<h2>Latest Entries</h2>
<ul>
  {% for entry in collections.all | reverse %}
    <li>
      <h3><a href="{{ entry.url }}">{{ entry.data.title }}</a></h3>
      <p><time datetime="{{ entry.date | date('YYYY-MM-DD') }}">{{ entry.date | date('MMMM YYYY') }}</time> - {{ entry.data.location }}</p>
      <p>{{ entry.content | truncate(200) }}</p>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

<h2>How to Contribute</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Clone this repository</li>
  <li>Copy the template from <code>_data/template.md</code></li>
  <li>Fill in the details for your entry</li>
  <li>Save the file with a descriptive name and date (e.g., <code>1952-harry-benjamin.md</code>)</li>
  <li>Run <code>npm run build</code> to generate the site</li>
  <li>Create a pull request with your changes</li>
</ol>
